msgid ""
"But we might find a compromise in between: for me, making bread is a "
"troublesome task. Grinding the blackroots and corn to flour and then baking "
"the bread is tedious and boring; I feel a more industrial approach would be "
"helpful here. I for one would love to just have fresh bread delivered to my "
"house every day."
msgstr "Ach ’s dòcha gun gabh seo rèiteachadh: chan e dèanamh arain ach buaireasach dhomh. Tha e ràsanach ’s bheir e ùine fhada fhada flùr a bhleith às na freumhagan ’s a’ choirce agus aran fhuineadh dheth an uairsin; saoilidh mi gum bhiodh gnìomhachas feumail airson sin. Bheireadh e toileachas mòr dhomhsa nan lìbhrigte aran ùr blàth dhan taigh agam gach latha."
